H3.text: The Hotel Matignon is the official residence of the Prime Minister of which European country. FRANCE

A4.text: The Hôtel Matignon (French: Hôtel de Matignon, pronounced [otɛl d(ə) matiɲɔ̃]) is the official residence of the Prime Minister of France.

A5.text: It is located in the 7th arrondissement of Paris, at 57 Rue de Varenne.
